snippet.title: Street Fighter X Tekken - First Look
snippet.description:
Like Street Fighter X Tekken http://on.fb.me/pb9YQ7 and enter the contest on Facebook for a shot at a PS3. Join the fight on Twitter: http://bit.ly/sQtLPK

The Dragon and the Devil himself finally collides and sets the stage for fighting legends in this long-anticipated FINAL FIGHT!
